{"changed": true, "stdout": "\n============================================================\n  PRE-CHECK \u2014 Detecting Active SSH Port\n============================================================\n   Trying port 22...\n\u2705 Switch is reachable on port 22\n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 1 \u2014 Enable SSH & Change Port to 25  (via port 22)\n============================================================\n\n[Step 1] Connect to switch as admin on port 22\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\u2705 Admin SSH connected on port 22\n\n[Step 2] Enable SSH server  \u2192  ip ssh\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\u2705 SSH enabled globally\n\n[Step 3] Change SSH port to 25  \u2192  ip ssh port 25\n------------------------------------------------------------\n   \u26a0\ufe0f  Changing port restarts SSH service \u2014 current session will drop.\n\u2705 Port change sent \u2014 session dropped by switch (expected)\n   \u23f3 Waiting 5s for SSH service to restart on port 25...\n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 2 \u2014 Reconnect on Port 25 & Verify\n============================================================\n\n[Step 4] Reconnect as admin on new port 25\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\u2705 Admin SSH reconnected on port 25\n\n[Step 5] Verify port change  \u2192  show ip ssh\n------------------------------------------------------------\nshow ip ssh\r\nSwitch SSH is enabled\r\nSwitch SSH port is 25\r\n# \n  SSH enabled        : \u2705 YES\n  Port = 25 reflected : \u2705 YES\n\n[Step 6] show users\n------------------------------------------------------------\nshow users\r\nLine is vty 0.\r\n    * You are at this line now.\r\n    Connection is from 192.168.180.69:38720 by SSH.\r\n    User name is admin.\r\n    Privilege is 15.\r\n    Elapsed time is 0 day 0 hour 0 min 3 sec.\r\n    Idle time is 0 day 0 hour 0 min 0 sec.\r\n\r\n# \n\n\u2705 Admin session (port 25) closed\n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 3 \u2014 Verify Port 22 is NO LONGER Accessible\n============================================================\n\n[Step 7] Attempt SSH on old port 22  (should FAIL)\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\u2705 Port 22 correctly REJECTED\n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 4 \u2014 External Client SSH on Custom Port 25\n============================================================\n\n[Step 8] Login as admin on port 25\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\u2705 External SSH login SUCCESSFUL on port 25\n\n[Step 9] show ip ssh\n------------------------------------------------------------\nshow ip ssh\r\nSwitch SSH is enabled\r\nSwitch SSH port is 25\r\n# \n\n[Step 10] show users\n------------------------------------------------------------\nshow users\r\nLine is vty 0.\r\n    * You are at this line now.\r\n    Connection is from 192.168.180.69:40540 by SSH.\r\n    User name is admin.\r\n    Privilege is 15.\r\n    Elapsed time is 0 day 0 hour 0 min 3 sec.\r\n    Idle time is 0 day 0 hour 0 min 0 sec.\r\n\r\n# \n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 5 \u2014 Device-Side SSH Client on Port 25\n============================================================\n\n[Step 11] Connect on port 25 to run device-side ssh command\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n[Step 12] Run  \u2192  ssh admin 192.168.180.155 port 25\n------------------------------------------------------------\nssh admin 192.168.180.155 port 25\r\n\r\r\nHost '192.168.180.155' is not in the trusted hosts file.\r\r\n(ssh-rsa fingerprint SHA256:IyPlXHvdC5bdIvKJsVr1DTENu63zKbAcpqH6go2wdVo)\r\r\nDo you want to continue connecting? (y/n) \n\u2705 Device-side SSH client reached switch on custom port\n\n============================================================\n  PHASE 6 \u2014 Cleanup: Restore Default Port 22\n============================================================\n\n[Step 13] Connect on port 25 and restore to port 22\n------------------------------------------------------------\n   \u23f3 Waiting 5s for SSH to restart on port 22...\nshow ip ssh\r\nSwitch SSH is enabled\r\nSwitch SSH port is 22\r\n# \n\u2705 SSH port restored to 22\n\n============================================================\n  TEST SUMMARY\n============================================================\n  \u2705  Port 25 reflected in show ip ssh           PASS\n  \u2705  Old port 22 blocked                        PASS\n  \u2705  External client login port 25              PASS\n  \u2705  show ip ssh on port 25 session             PASS\n  \u2705  show users on port 25 session              PASS\n  \u2705  Device-side SSH client port 25             PASS\n  \u2705  Cleanup \u2014 port restored to 22              PASS\n\n\ud83c\udf89  ALL TESTS PASSED \n TEST-HFCL-SW-03 - Management - Verify SSH port Customization and SSH client support successfully passed\n============================================================", "stderr": "", "rc": 0, "cmd": ["timeout", "60", "/home/hfcl/jenkins-venv/bin/python", "/home/hfcl/management-test-automation-scripts/test3.py", "192.168.180.155", "admin", "admin"], "start": "2026-03-19 17:35:42.080985", "end": "2026-03-19 17:36:32.322755", "delta": "0:00:50.241770", "msg": "", "invocation": {"module_args": {"_raw_params": "timeout 60 /home/hfcl/jenkins-venv/bin/python /home/hfcl/management-test-automation-scripts/test3.py 192.168.180.155 admin admin\n", "_uses_shell": false, "expand_argument_vars": true, "stdin_add_newline": true, "strip_empty_ends": true, "cmd": null, "argv": null, "chdir": null, "executable": null, "creates": null, "removes": null, "stdin": null}}}